-last-dinner-party@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jade-teddy-swims-the-last-dinner-party@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jade-teddy-swims-the-last-dinner-party@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jade-teddy-swims-the-last-dinner-party@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/brit-awards">2025年英国大奖</a>上的第一轮表演者已被揭露 - 请参阅以下当前的行为清单。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-nominees-3831514">这是2025年英国奖的所有提名人</a></strong></li></ul><p>今天（1月31日），英国颁奖典礼宣布了即将举行的颁奖典礼的前五位表演者，该颁奖典礼<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/date-revealed-for-the-brit-awards-2025-3794739">将于3月1日星期六在伦敦的O2举行</a>，并专门在ITV1和ITVX上播出。</p><p>到目前为止宣布的是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jade-thirlwall">Jade</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shaboozey">Shaboozey</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/teddy-swims">Teddy游泳</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">最后的晚宴</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/myles-smith">Myles Smith</a> ，其中最后一个在12月被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-name-2025-rising-star-winner-3819335">宣布为2025年Rising Star的Brit Awards奖</a>。史密斯还获得了另外三个奖项的提名：最佳新艺术家，年度歌曲和流行音乐表演。</p><p>像史密斯一样，宣布的其他四个表演者也在颁奖典礼上获得了多个奖项。杰德（Jade）参加了年度歌曲和流行音乐表演，而最后一场晚宴则是为万事达卡专辑，年度最佳新艺术家和替代/摇滚表演提名的。 </p><figure id="attachment_3830430" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3830430" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3830430" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/JADE-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Michael-Loccisano_Getty-Images.jpg" alt="玉" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/JADE-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Michael-Loccisano_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/JADE-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Michael-Loccisano_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/JADE-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Michael-Loccisano_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/JADE-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Michael-Loccisano_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/JADE-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Michael-Loccisano_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/JADE-CREDIT_-Photo-by-Michael-Loccisano_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3830430" class="wp-caption-text"> Jade Thirlwall  - 信用：Michael Loccisano/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>泰迪游泳的“失落控制”被提名为年度国际歌曲，而Shaboozey则在同一类别中提名为“ bar Song（Tipsy）”  -<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-nominees-3831514">在此处查看提名的完整列表</a>。</p><p>预计将在三月份的颁奖典礼上宣布更多行为。喜剧演员和演员 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-jack-whitehall-to-return-as-host-3829454">杰克·怀特霍尔（Jack Whitehall）被宣布为返回的主持人</a>，这是他在2018年，2019年，2020年和2021年举行的第五次举行仪式。</p><p>今年的最高候选人是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a> ，他以五个点头领先，包括年度艺术家，流行音乐和舞蹈表演。她与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">比利·埃里什（Billie Eilish</a> ）的“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-billie-eilish-guess-remix-the-dare-finneas-3780251">猜测”（Guess）</a>的合作也将参加年度最佳歌曲，而她的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-review-lyrics-tracklist-3762875">“小子”</a>唱片已入围年度万事达卡专辑。 </p><figure id="attachment_3825112" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3825112" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3825112" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024_charlixcx_getty_2000x1270.jpg" alt="Charli XCX" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024_charlixcx_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024_charlixcx_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024_charlixcx_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024_charlixcx_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024_charlixcx_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/2024_charlixcx_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3825112" class="wp-caption-text"> Charli XCX在2024年12月12日在好莱坞的TCL中国剧院参加了洛杉矶的首映礼：Robyn Beck/AFP通过Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>今年也提名的是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-cure">CURE</a> ，他们因<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-cure-songs-of-a-lost-world-review-lyrics-3801637">“失落的世界的歌曲”</a>获得了三十年来获得第一个英国人提名 - 他们将获得年度专辑，年度最佳专辑和Alt/Rock Act。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-beatles">甲壳虫乐队</a>还与万事达卡（Mastercard）一起被提名为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-beatles-final-song-now-and-then-3529039">“当时”</a> 。</p><p>年度最佳制片人的获奖者和年度最佳词曲作者将在以后宣布。</p><p>早在11月，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/new-brit-award-trophy-design-for-2025-revealed-3814651">新的奖杯设计就在2025年的仪式前揭晓</a>。它是由著名的不列颠尼日利亚多学科艺术家加布里埃尔·摩西（Gabriel Moses）创建的，他多年来一直与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/skepta">Skepta</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/little-simz">Little Simz</a> ，Burberry等人合作。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2025-first-performers-revealed-3833403">Brit Post Awards 2025：首次表演者透露，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
